      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or for parts. The exterior has significant rust along the rocker panels and wheel wells, along with several deep scratches and a large dent in the rear passenger door. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and likely needs a head gasket replacement, and the transmission shifts harshly between gears. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional air conditioning system. It will require a trailer for transport as it is not currently roadworthy.",
