    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hi there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a great car! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it's ready to hit the road with its next owner immediately. It runs beautifully and is perfect if you're looking for something reliable and comfy without the brand-new price tag. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This high-revving powerplant delivers a linear torque curve up to its 7,900 RPM redline. Essential preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity. The Double VANOS system has been recalibrated for precise valve timing, and the 6-speed manual transmission shifts with crisp engagement. Equipped with a factory limited-slip differential and a suspension tuned for neutral handling, this chassis remains tight and responsive. While it exhibits minor cosmetic evidence of spirited road use, the drivetrain and cooling system are optimized for performance longevity.",
